ygData.subject: Re: Firey Avenger
ygData.msgSnippet: Kedge has not been explored to my knowledge.  The fish guarding the entrance.  THE ENTRANCE.  are lvl 32.  Can t imagine the stuff you would find right inside.
ygData.messageBody:
Kedge has not been explored to my knowledge. The fish guarding the
entrance. THE ENTRANCE. are lvl 32. Can't imagine the stuff you would
find right inside. If you have been in guk the stuff at the entrance is
simple and the stuff inside just gets harder. Kedge would be . . . not
welcoming =)
